::Hot Rod::

He arrived at the room.
"What is it Epyon?"

::Epyon::

"Look at this message on the comp."

Hot Rod watches the message.
"I'm up for it."

"I already registered. Here you can send a message," said Epyon.

"Ok." Hot Rod walks to the comp and starts recording.
"This is the Autobot Transformer Hot Rod. I am from Iron Raptor's
Maximals. I would like to enter your regular competition."
He sent the message. 
"Ok, Epyon, lets get back to training."

"I cant. I'm watching Eyebright for Starice."

"Babysiting? Ok, c'ya later." Hot Rod walks out of the room, and laughs
at the thought of the Star Ship Captain watching a kid. He then makes
his way back to where he left IR. He stalks in silence, so he is not
attacked.
